name: after
trans: Coming later in time or following something.

name: big
trans: Large in size; not small.

name: cold
trans: Having a low temperature; not hot or warm.

name: day
trans: The time when it is light outside, from morning to night.

name: eat
trans: To put food in your mouth and swallow it.

name: fast
trans: Moving or happening quickly.

name: give
trans: To let someone have something.

name: home
trans: The place where you live.

name: inside
trans: In or into a building or container; not outside.

name: jumped
trans: Pushed yourself off the ground with your legs (past tense of jump).

name: keep
trans: To continue to have something; not to give it away.

name: little
trans: Small in size; not big.

name: make
trans: To create or build something.

name: night
trans: The time when it is dark outside and most people sleep.

name: open
trans: To move something so you can see or go through it.

name: play
trans: To have fun doing games or activities.

name: quick
trans: Fast; done in a short time.

name: rest
trans: To relax and stop working or moving.

name: sleep
trans: To close your eyes and rest your body and mind.

name: time
trans: When something happens, shown by clocks and watches.

name: understand
trans: To know what something means.

name: voice
trans: The sound you make when you speak or sing.

name: walk
trans: To move by putting one foot in front of the other.

name: xmas
trans: A short way to write Christmas.

name: young
trans: Not old; in the early part of life.

name: zoo
trans: A place where wild animals are kept for people to see.

name: air
trans: The invisible gas around us that we breathe.

name: blue
trans: A color like the sky or the ocean.

name: come
trans: To move toward someone or something.

name: down
trans: Moving toward a lower place.

name: end
trans: The last part of something; when something finishes.

name: farm
trans: A place where people grow food and raise animals.

name: green
trans: A color like grass and leaves.

name: here
trans: In this place; where you are now.

name: in
trans: Inside something or a place.

name: joy
trans: A feeling of great happiness.

name: kindly
trans: In a nice and caring way.

name: look
trans: To use your eyes to see something.

name: man
trans: An adult male person.

name: nice
trans: Pleasant and good; kind and friendly.

name: over
trans: Above something or on top of it.

name: pink
trans: A light red color.

name: quietly
trans: In a way that makes little or no noise.

name: round
trans: Shaped like a circle or ball.

name: small
trans: Little in size; not big.

name: take
trans: To get hold of something and move it.

name: until
trans: Up to the time when something happens.

name: visit
trans: To go to see someone or a place.

name: white
trans: A color like snow or milk.

name: xenon
trans: A type of gas used in some lights.

name: yesterday
trans: The day before today.

name: zeroes
trans: More than one zero; the number 0 written many times.

name: again
trans: One more time; another time.

name: black
trans: The darkest color, like the night sky.

name: can
trans: To be able to do something.

name: does
trans: A word used to ask questions or talk about what someone performs.

name: each
trans: Every one of a group.

name: fun
trans: Something that is enjoyable and makes you happy.

name: great
trans: Very good or wonderful.

name: help
trans: To make something easier for someone or do something for them.

name: into
trans: Moving to the inside of something.

name: join
trans: To become part of a group or to connect things together.

name: know
trans: To have information about something in your mind.

name: last
trans: Coming at the end; the final one.

name: more
trans: A greater amount or number.

name: near
trans: Close to something; not far away.

name: other
trans: Different from the one you have; additional ones.

name: part
trans: A piece of something; not the whole thing.

name: question
trans: Something you ask when you want to know information.

name: read
trans: To look at words and understand them.

name: six
trans: The number 6.

name: two
trans: The number 2.

name: upon
trans: On top of something.

name: very
trans: A word that means really or a lot.

name: will
trans: A word used to talk about the future.

name: xylophone
trans: A musical instrument with bars that you hit with small hammers to make sounds.

name: your
trans: Belonging to you.

name: zebra
trans: An animal that looks like a horse with black and white stripes.

name: about
trans: On the subject of; concerning something.

name: before
trans: Earlier in time; happening first.

name: call
trans: To say something in a loud voice or to telephone someone.

name: door
trans: Something you open and close to go in and out of a room or building.

name: even
trans: Flat and smooth; or used to emphasize something surprising.

name: find
trans: To discover or see something you were looking for.

name: goodbye
trans: A word you say when you leave someone.

name: happy
trans: Feeling joy and pleasure; not sad.

name: ice
trans: Frozen water that is hard and cold.

name: job
trans: Work that someone does to earn money.

name: kick
trans: To hit something with your foot.

name: longer
trans: More long; taking more time or distance.

name: many
trans: A large number of things or people.

name: next
trans: Coming right after this one; the one that follows.

name: once
trans: One time; happening one time only.

name: people
trans: More than one person; human beings.

name: rainy
trans: When rain is falling from the sky.

name: see
trans: To use your eyes to look at something.

name: three
trans: The number 3.

name: us
trans: Me and other people; you and I together.

name: village
trans: A small town in the country with houses and shops.

name: winter
trans: The coldest season of the year.
